onLineSrc.orDesc: Information from Oneida County Land Information Office

dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Oneida County, Wisconsin in 2019.[Direct observation of PLSS corners with survey grade GPS by various contractors.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[To establish tighter control points for Public Land Survey System section corners.]
